The game picks up where Hexen left off. Haing finally obtained the
chaos Sphere, you find yourself suddenly transported to the Realm
of the Dead where the sphere is powerless. To escape the unholy,
evil world and rerurn to the land of the living, you must journey
through a blighted wilderness and layiege to the mighty Citadel of
the Deathking. In their destruction lies the nly passage to true
freedom.
